[Student "S"]
{NORTH has a balanced hand with 23 points. He opens 2\C and expects to rebid 2NT.

SOUTH has 12 points so makes a positive response in her best suit. Since that suit is 
\Ds she must jump to the 3-level. 

NORTH now describes his balanced, minimum hand by bidding 3NT.

SOUTH bids 6NT, knowing that the partnership holds at least 34 points.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
